<div class="ak_all">
    <script type="text/javascript">
        function fetchAcademician(obj) {
            var menuID = $(obj).attr("AkademisyenID");
            var dil = $(obj).attr("dil");
            var url = '../../../_layouts/AkademikKadroV2/Akademisyen.aspx?AkademisyenID=' + menuID + '&amp;Dil=' + dil;
            $.post(url, function (data) {
                $(".BolumOzet").html(data);
                $(this).appendTo($(".BolumOzet"));
                $("#akademisyenler").hide();
                $("#genelveriler").show();
                $(".fakulte_rsm").hide();
                $("#akademisyenler").css("position", "absolute");
                $("#genelveriler").css("position", "relative");
            });
            $(".hLink").removeClass("ak_site_aktif");
            $(obj).addClass("ak_site_aktif");
        }

        function fetchData(obj) {
            var menuID = $(obj).attr("menuid");
            var dil = $(obj).attr("dil");
            var url = '../../../_layouts/AkademikKadroV2/MenuContent.aspx?MenuID=' + menuID + '&amp;Dil=' + dil;
            try {
                $.post(url, function (data) {
                    $(".BolumOzet").html(data);
                    $("#akademisyenler").hide();
                    $("#genelveriler").show();
                    $(".fakulte_rsm").show();
                    $("#akademisyenler").css("position", "absolute");
                    $("#genelveriler").css("position", "relative");
                });
            } catch (e) {

            }
            $(".hLink").removeClass("ak_site_aktif");
            $(obj).addClass("ak_site_aktif");
        }

        $(document).ready(function () {
            $("#akademisyenler").css("position", "absolute");
            $("#genelveriler").css("position", "relative");
        });

        function akademisyenGoster() {
            $("#akademisyenler").css("position", "relative");
            $("#genelveriler").css("position", "absolute");
            $("#akademisyenler").show();
            $("#genelveriler").hide();
            $(".hLink").removeClass("ak_site_aktif");
            $("#akademisURL").addClass("ak_site_aktif");
            return false;
        }
    </script>

            <div style="overflow: hidden" class="fakulte_rsm">
                <img id="ctl00_m_g_4cacd6f2_0d30_4a7e_ac28_82434140f6f8_ctl00_bolumAltResim" src="http://www.sehir.edu.tr/SiteAssets/Pages/Akademik/Gorseller/bilgisayar_muh.png" />
            </div>
            <div class="fakulte_ack">
                <span class="BolumOzet" id="ctl00_m_g_4cacd6f2_0d30_4a7e_ac28_82434140f6f8_ctl00_BolumOzet"><p style="font-family:arial;font-size:9pt;color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">?</p>
<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">
</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:9pt;color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">
</span><p style="font-family:arial;font-size:9pt;color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">Computer scientists have an important role in designing powerful 
systems that measure physical output, convert the measurement to data 
and the data to information, and present this information to the benefit
 of humanity. In developing the information technologies of the future, 
the world needs creative and innovative young computer scientists and 
computer engineers. Faculty members and researchers of the Department of
 Computer Science and Engineering of Ýstanbul Þehir University have come
 together with the awareness of this need. 
</p>
<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">
</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:9pt;color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">
</span><div style="font-family:arial;font-size:9pt;color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">In our curriculum formed jointly with the Department of Electrical 
and Electronics Engineering, our aim is to help the students acquire an 
integral approach to the problems in the field of engineering. At our 
department, an international education awaits the students, which will 
prepare them in the best way to solve the computer science and computer 
engineering problems in the industrial and public domains and especially
 to a Ph.D. education on a more advanced level. <br /><br /></div>
<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">
</span><span style="font-family:arial;font-size:9pt;color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">
</span><div style="font-family:arial;font-size:9pt;color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">At the Department of Computer Science and Engineering, founded on 
intellectual and academic freedom, students will learn to take risks and
 be open to brave initiatives. The research fields in our department 
include distributed computing, cryptography, advanced database systems, 
cloud computing, social media and artificial intelligence. In addition, 
students will gain exposure to engineering ethics, engineering processes
 and entrepreneurship, and will gain a foundation that is serious, 
strong, theoretical and based on practice. They will graduate from the 
Department of Computer Science and Engineering with knowledge and skills
 to make abstraction and analysis, with a high capacity for design and 
solution.</div>
<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">
</span>
<p><br /></p></span>
